                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Hello,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;The time has finally arrived - your 10X Health Genetic Test results are now available!&amp;nbsp;We have attached a PDF copy of your personalized report (password protected). You will separately receive an email with the password to access the file.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Don&amp;#39;t want to wait for the password email? &lt;/b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://portal.10xhealthsystem.com/session/signin?return_url=%2F&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;CLICK HERE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;view your results directly in your secure patient portal.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;In the report you will find:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Summary of your genetic test results, including any variants.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Detailed description of each of the 5 genes tested.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Explanation of how these genes impact your body&amp;rsquo;s ability to break down key nutrients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Personalized 10X Health Supplement Protocol based on your results.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Within your report, you will find your personalized supplementation protocol&amp;nbsp;that will include all the vital nutrients and elements your body may be missing based on your genetic information.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Your report is designed to be self-guided, but if you prefer to schedule a live consultation with a 10X Health Wellness Expert to look over your information and answer questions, you can do so &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://shop.10xhealthsystem.com/products/genetic-breakthrough-session-clarity-call&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;here&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;With this new genetic test information, you have taken an important step forward on your wellness journey and we are here to support you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Yours in optimal wellness,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wellness Team at&amp;nbsp;10&lt;span style=&quot;color:#cc0000;&quot;&gt;X&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Health&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Main: (844) 977-2810&lt;br /&gt;
Fax: (786) 598-8612&lt;br /&gt;
Email: support@10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

